  "response": "Here are some reliable sources for Twitter statistics by country:\n\n1. Statista\n- Offers comprehensive global social media usage data\n- Provides detailed Twitter user statistics by country\n- Paid and free access options\n\n2. Social Blade\n- Tracks social media statistics globally\n- Offers Twitter-specific country data\n- Free basic information available\n\n3. Datareportal\n- Annual digital reports with social media usage statistics\n- Includes Twitter user numbers by country\n- Free global reports\n\n4. We Are Social\n- Annual digital reports with social media insights\n- Comprehensive country-level statistics\n- Free reports available\n\n5. Twitter Official Blog\n- Occasionally publishes user statistics\n- Less frequent but authoritative source\n\n6. Hootsuite Digital Reports\n- Annual global social media reports\n- Country-specific Twitter usage data\n- Free executive summaries\n\n7. World Bank / Internet World Stats\n- Provides broader internet and social media penetration statistics\n- Can help contextualize Twitter usage\n\nMost of these sources update their statistics annually, so check the most recent reports for the most accurate information.",
